Setting Up Flask:
pip install flask flask_sqlalchemy flask_marshmallow
Flask App Structure:
project_management/
    ├── app.py
    ├── models.py
    ├── schemas.py
    ├── routes/
        ├── projects.py
        ├── tasks.py
        ├── teams.py
        ├── notifications.py
    ├── config.py
    └── __init__.py

